<plot>In 2004 a beast suddenly appears on a small island in the Finnish archipelago. It's winter and not much is going on in the community and this is seen as big news. The people on the island are afraid, they see tracks in the snow and find bloody remains of their poor house cats. Anonymous letters are sent to the local magazines and everybody debates the beast. Shall it be shot or saved? Politicians, hunters and the people on the island - everybody has an opinion.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?340404</url></doc>
